{
  "stem": "14387.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were well aware of everything, but we never dreamed-- never dreamed-- until the night of April the 9th that Norway would be invaded.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was never any thought of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went-- we were tired, went to bed as we usually did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, during the night, we heard planes flying overhead.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I mean-- the planes, we thought, what on earth is going on?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So many planes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we turned on the radio, and we heard that Germany had invaded Norway.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we immediately called my husband's brother, who lives in the-- lived in the central part of the town, and he said there were Nazis, there were Germans, wearing swastikas walking through the streets.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we knew what had happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the next morning, the whole family gathered.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Remember, they were a huge family-- nine brothers-- 10 brothers and sisters, nine boys and two girls, and we all met at his mother's house.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what are we going to do?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we decided-- it was decided that we would leave right away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were seven stores there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They closed the stores, and we didn't even go into the stores that morning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And decided-- there were several children, three or four of the brothers were married, I think there were two single-- with two single brothers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They decided that we would all go, except the single men.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The single men would stay and try to join the army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we thought, well, England is never going to allow Germany to stay in Norway.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're going to come and rescue us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were so sure that this was just going to be a temporary thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, my mother-in-law did not want to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
